# Premium Utilitarian Design Direction

## Audience

Facility managers, industrial directors, and commercial property owners. Design must communicate OSHA compliance, durability, and trust — not creativity or playfulness.

## Design System Reference

All tokens are defined in the [index.css](mdc:src/index.css) `@theme` block. Do not introduce new color or spacing values outside this system.

## Visual Language

- **Corners**: 0px border-radius everywhere — sharp, mechanical, industrial
- **Shadows**: Hard brutal box-shadows, no soft glows
- **Spacing**: 8dp grid system, disciplined alignment in header/footer/hero compositions
- **Transitions**: Snappy, mechanical motion via [motion.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/motion.tsx) — no floaty or ornamental animation
- **Contrast**: WCAG AA+ minimum, high-contrast text on dark backgrounds

## Typography

- **Display**: Barlow Condensed (`font-display`) — heavy, uppercase headings
- **Body**: Public Sans (`font-sans`) — USWDS-grade legibility
- Strong hierarchy with uppercase display treatment and direct content structure

